{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3522010/extras/EarlLogoRunner.png?t=1739320065\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Earl the Tomb Robber is\u00a0a story-driven adventure set on a mysterious &quot;Island of the Dead&quot;, full of rewarding exploration, challenging puzzles and cozy combat. After an ancient curse binds Earl to the ghost of a long deceased King, Earl must the break into the tombs and graves of the sacred island to recover the scattered mummified body parts of the cursed King.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>This game is as much about exploring exotic locations and mysterious tombs as it is about exploring your own personality and discovering how to identify your true authentic self. As Earl learns to face his own insecurities, can you do the same?</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>CHALLENGE!</strong></i></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Raid mysterious tombs and solve challenging puzzles to break an ancient curse and come away with untold riches!</i></p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>ENGAGE!</strong></i></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Navigate your away around the spirited inhabitants of The Island of the Dead, or attack them head on!</i></p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>EXPLORE!</strong></i></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Explore exotic locations while discovering the secrets of the island natives, and discovering yourself in the process.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3522010/extras/ComingSoon.jpg?t=1739320065\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/ste